Package: NestedWGCNA
Title: Two-Stage Gene Co-Expression Network Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dai <daiki@example.com>
Description: R implementation of a two-stage gene co-expression workflow.
    The package discovers coarse-grained modules (CGMs), extracts core genes,
    applies GenFocus normalization, and discovers fine-grained modules (FGMs).
    It also includes reproducible real-data case-study pipelines and pkgdown
    documentation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://dai540.github.io/NestedWGCNA, https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA
BugReports: https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
